{"tid":685752,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求兩隻PC GAME","createTime":"2018-05-31T16:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T22:48:47.000Z","uid":38745,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb79c303ed1368ce7fc6eb9ac1320f957688665a","tid":685752,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"有無人玩過《翡翠群星大贏家》同埋《瘋狂搖搖杯》呢兩隻PC game?<br />\n而家無聊無嘢做 回憶返細細個好鐘意玩呢兩隻game<br />\n所以想down落mac嚟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可能真係太舊 所以搵極都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235552_4072bc3f716e2a58932bfee57692bf7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235552_4072bc3f716e2a58932bfee57692bf7d.jpg&h=79308950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻game要碟 以前試過想搵 但都搵唔到<br />\n超得意 啲配音仲好過癮<br />\n細個同表哥表姐玩得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235658_3c1a3fa918874237ecfa6eab89a3d22e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235658_3c1a3fa918874237ecfa6eab89a3d22e.jpg&h=c8ace021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n表姐介紹嘅遊戲<br />\n好鐘意撳啲路人同埋自己設計飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前啲遊戲可能無咁精緻 但都好有趣味性<br />\n同埋同表兄表姐一齊玩嘅日子原來已經係好耐好耐以前<br />\n而家大個咗可以聚埋一齊嘅日子真係好少好少<br />\n諗返都會好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e24895e1786f54d2f16a8e352ecf924e9bafc7a","tid":685752,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eddeccfe303038295c98667a1c312dc5c579454e","tid":685752,"uid":95542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"搖搖杯幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca98a4805febe48dc5e6a2e15f29bf78a19672e7","tid":685752,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eddeccfe303038295c98667a1c312dc5c579454e","tid":685752,"uid":95542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"搖搖杯幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾正"},{"pid":"abd62ceed745d3be80f6b37ce91570fc8f73a1f4","tid":685752,"uid":48276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca98a4805febe48dc5e6a2e15f29bf78a19672e7","tid":685752,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eddeccfe303038295c98667a1c312dc5c579454e","tid":685752,"uid":95542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"搖搖杯幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"便利商店果班人做？"},{"pid":"c6a9dec7ed89f13e160ddf806d3f744c7d78dedb","tid":685752,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T23:45:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73e89ae16598fed883b60092717c8014b73dcda","tid":685752,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T00:12:58.000Z","msg":"瘋狂搖搖杯我好似仲有keep隻碟"},{"pid":"1f0c0a8a005934e36672ebb792f3818fff412967","tid":685752,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c73e89ae16598fed883b60092717c8014b73dcda","tid":685752,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T00:12:58.000Z","msg":"瘋狂搖搖杯我好似仲有keep隻碟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:50:27.000Z","msg":"有無辦法係mac用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8267663f2f940bb40ed57072256d566cf02aabee","tid